{"tid":449564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十多名中國警察砸店 持警棍鐵鏟圍毆平民","createTime":"2017-10-27T09:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T13:40:38.000Z","uid":75969,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"c77c16d7944a77f5fd130c57cf68cc903a3c1485","tid":449564,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpgJLC0o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpgJLC0o.jpg&h=98e54c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一群中國警察衝到小吃店裡持警棍與鐵鏟圍毆平民。（圖擷取自影片）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國與台灣除了政治環境上大相逕庭外，國家發展也常被人拿來做比較的對象，爭論哪一方比較「進步」。而近期網路上流傳一段影片，十多名中國公安竟直接衝入餐館持器物毆打平民，被打的女店員只能倒在地上哭泣，毫無反擊能力，貼出影片的人則表示：「將來台灣被統後，台灣商戶們也同樣要這麼面對中共的執法隊。」<br />\n<br />\n 名為「記錄中國」的臉書社團中，一名網友於23日貼出了一段令人瞠目結舌的影片。多達13名中國警察直接衝進餐館中，先與一名女店員發生拉扯，隨後警察翻了桌子，並直接一拳往另一名男店員臉上揍下去，甚至還拿出警棍與巨大的鐵鏟來痛毆三名店員。其中一名店員不堪多名壯碩警察毆打，當下不支倒地。<br />\n<br />\n而其中一名樣貌兇狠的警察作勢警告後帶著一群警察離開，女店員擁著倒地的男店員，並開始撥電話，另一名勉強站著的男店員也只能氣憤看著這些「不法之徒」離去，想不到此時一群警方再度衝了回來，拿起警棍再次連續毆打男店員，而女店員只好抱著男店員，並努力護住他的頭。<br />\n<br />\n更諷刺的是，這個影片的配樂正是中國的愛國歌曲《社會主義好》，原為讚揚毛澤東所帶領的中國，但此曲在文化大革命之後消失。而2012年中國出現唱紅歌熱潮，此歌又被中宣部定為「百首愛國主義」歌曲之一。而網友看完影片紛紛痛批：「警察公然私闖民宅，傷害無辜老百姓！這跟北韓沒兩樣，比起來isis差遠了」、「這個就是中國」、「這就是文明執法」、「這就是人民子弟軍？習大大中國夢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yj2IfqCJ3ZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyj2IfqCJ3ZQ&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=54ced0bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yj2IfqCJ3ZQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2235006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2235006&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=609b1597\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2235006&h=5da46d7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2235006</a>"},{"pid":"a140f94a637498637dcc75e2c8b42fdca37fb054","tid":449564,"uid":95,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:59:31.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨，全球最大黑社會。"},{"pid":"bd58aab777fe765dc3cfc7384b124808d855fb89","tid":449564,"uid":36162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"宜家公安入去食嘢重駛唔駛俾錢?"},{"pid":"a79f13685083a3285b4d2d47880b9744dab95bdc","tid":449564,"uid":53687,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"全國最大犯罪集團上線了"},{"pid":"0f1670357e70159676aa29c153d8facfd726a792","tid":449564,"uid":57513,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家公安入去食嘢重駛唔駛俾錢?</blockquote><br />\n老闆比錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c15f77aa67fbcd3925fbb6d6989134ac169f2b","tid":449564,"uid":32325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"不愧為全球最大嘅黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cae4b99cddb164e4fffb2bbd6db7a64e6291dc3","tid":449564,"uid":16567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"打得好！賤民抵打，打死佢就啱啦"},{"pid":"951e1db47aad3ac87e74ea13888465c097e3d232","tid":449564,"uid":112581,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"冇做錯野比人打怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25f3bfe96c89c80a4b8977edad058c7fca18d5a","tid":449564,"uid":56432,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"中國人已經進步很多了，以前張獻忠男殺女姦㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{